          ]
        },
        {
          "sentence": "In 1941, Ruth was the soprano soloist in a performance of Johann Sebastian Bach's wedding cantata Weichet nur at Huntington Chambers Hall in Boston, a concert sponsored by the Composer's Forum",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "She assisted the choral music composer, arranger, and conductor S",
          "refs": [
            "https://archive.org/details/sim_music-magazine-and-musical-courier_1941-03-01_123_5/page/32/mode/1up?q=%22Joan+Ruth%22"
