        },
        {
          "sentence": "G",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
          "sentence": "Braslavsky in a lecture on \"Jewish music and music by Jews\" given at the Boston Public Library at Copley Square on January 31, 1943, performing several traditional Jewish songs and music by Jewish composers to provide attendees examples during the lecture",
          "refs": []
        },
        {
